Project Name: Hospital API

Tools used: Python, Fast-API, 
Editor: Visual Studio Code

Setup Instructions:

1. Create a folder 

2. Open the folder using Visual Studio Code

3. Open Terminal

4. Install fast-api framework using the command "pip install fastapi[standard]"

5. Open extensions on the left tab and type fast-api extensions and install it

6. Create a python folder main.py and type the required codes

7. Finally run the code by pressing F5 and select the debugger as fast-api

8. Then at the terminal open the link http://127.0.0.1:8000/ to open the browser

9. Then open http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs to view the API

10. To stop the server press contol + C at the terminal
    
